name: Brendan Sullivan
text: There pizza is decent, and you can get your pizza fairly quick, but in a town that seems to only have pizza shops its hard for Pizza Hut to stand out.  For quality and taste, I would probably choose a different location; although for price they are very affordable.

name: Avo Shahverdian
text: It's a pizza hut so don't expect gourmet. But service is good, pizzas made well. Stuffed crust is legit.
